<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<e:Skin class="BeginGame" width="640" height="960" xmlns:e="http://ns.egret.com/eui" xmlns:w="http://ns.egret.com/wing">
	<e:Image source="1_jpg" bottom="0"/>
	<e:Button id="eatBtn" label="" x="235" y="719" rotation="0" width="175" height="150" alpha="0">
		<e:skinName>
		<e:Skin states="up,down,disabled">
			<e:Image width="100%" height="100%" source="again_png"/>
			<e:Label id="labelDisplay" horizontalCenter="0" verticalCenter="0"/>
		</e:Skin>
		</e:skinName>
	</e:Button>
	<e:Image id="bg" source="loading_jpg" y="0"/>
</e:Skin>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<e:Skin class="GameEnd" width="640" height="960" xmlns:e="http://ns.egret.com/eui" xmlns:w="http://ns.egret.com/wing">
	<e:Image source="bg_jpg" left="0" right="0" top="0" bottom="0" locked="true"/>
	<e:Image source="result_png" x="0" y="0" locked="true"/>
	<e:Button id="shareBtn" label="" x="127" y="689" locked="true">
		<e:skinName>
			<e:Skin states="up,down,disabled">
			<e:Image width="100%" height="100%" source="share_btn_png"/>
			<e:Label id="labelDisplay" horizontalCenter="0" verticalCenter="0"/>
			</e:Skin>
		</e:skinName>
	</e:Button>
	<e:Button id="aginBtn" label="" x="340" y="689" locked="true">
		<e:skinName>
			<e:Skin states="up,down,disabled">
			<e:Image width="100%" height="100%" source="again_png"/>
			<e:Label id="labelDisplay" horizontalCenter="0" verticalCenter="0"/>
			</e:Skin>
		</e:skinName>
	</e:Button>
	<e:Label id="result" text="成绩" y="580" textColor="0xfc7474" minWidth="400" textAlign="center" fontFamily="Arial" horizontalCenter="0" bold="true" locked="true"/>
	<e:Group id="mask_group" width="640" height="960" x="0" y="0" visible="false">
		<e:Image source="share_png" x="0" y="0"/>
	</e:Group>
</e:Skin>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<e:Skin class="PlayGame" width="640" height="960" xmlns:e="http://ns.egret.com/eui" xmlns:w="http://ns.egret.com/wing">
	<e:Image source="bg_jpg" y="0" left="0"/>
	<e:Image id="food" source="green_png" y="359" horizontalCenter="0" anchorOffsetX="150" anchorOffsetY="150"/>
	<e:Image id="simg" source="green_png" x="13" y="10" anchorOffsetX="0" width="80" anchorOffsetY="0" height="80" alpha="0.75"/>
	<e:Label id="GameScore" text="得分" y="759" textColor="0x000000" horizontalCenter="0" textAlign="center" verticalAlign="middle" minWidth="150"/>
	<e:Label id="GameTime" text="时间" x="490" y="35" textColor="0x070707" verticalAlign="middle" textAlign="center" minWidth="150"/>
</e:Skin>
